reviewText: Nice item. Thanks for the prompt ship!
Wonderful nostalgic films.  I highly recommend!
I love getting 3 favorite movies in one package!

This is one of the best combo packs I've ever seen. Each movie is a classic in its own right and time, which works great for my mother who loves Sabrina, Me (I'm the genius!), and my little sister (the prince & me.)

I just adore Julia Ormand in Sabrina, her laugh,her giggle,and those stern looks when she quizzes others in the cast.
I.Q. has been a long time favorite of mine. Anything with Meg Ryan just ha to be good.

I was hoping to replace my VHS with DVD and was excited to find this 3 pack.  I was not able to view the movie IQ on two different DVD players because of a defective disk.  I requested a shipping label to send it back for a replacement.  I was able to send it back but Amazon wasn't able to send me a new DVD and credited my account.
